data.description: Welcome home. This home has it all.  This home has been completely re done. New Kitchen with stainless steel appliances. New gas range, new flooring and new granite counter tops. Beautiful wood floors upstairs and Bamboo floors in the lower family room.  All bathrooms have been upgraded with new tubs, vanities, sinks and title floors.  The roof and gutters replaced 2 years ago and have a warranty. there is a one car garage to keep your car out of the weather. Lighting has been upgraded throughout and has recessed lighting in most rooms. Just off the Waldorf bypass to make an easy commute to DC. Come view this wonderful home.
